data.description: Charming, 2021 built home on #18 tee box of the popular Wyboo Golf Course in gated Deercreek. The kitchen, dining & family room flow into one another for an open concept, perfect for entertaining & family gatherings. The kitchen boasts white cabinets, large center island, attractive backsplash, granite countertops, spacious pantry & SS appls. The owner's suite, located in the back for added privacy, features a tray ceiling, spacious walk-in closet, tiled shower, dual vanities & separate water closet. Relax on the rear patio & enjoy the golf course views. You'll appreciate the local golfing, numerous watersport activities on nearby Lake Marion or community swimming pool, library & fitness areas! Transferrable home warranty.
